  "lyrics": "When you see me through the tears.\nI'm in love with you.\nYou talkin' to me like you wanna be all over me, like you can get me through this. We got more than the world could keep this.\nI'll stand by you, yeah, yeah.\nI wanna go back with you, like we did in the past, baby.\nI'll keep on trying, trying, and trying.\nAin't nobody got me like that\nWhere you run to?\nWhere you want to? Where you want too?\nTo, where he gonna run to? Ghost in the man. Where he gonna lead to? The ghost in the mans.\nGhost in a man, where he don't run to. Ghost in a ma'am, where you don't running to. Sinner man.\nSineman, where you gonna run to? Oh, Sineman, Where you gonna Run to? Cosineman, Were you gonna\nCinderman, where he gonna run to? Cinderman, Where he gonna' run to?' Cinderman? Where he' gonna run\nWhere you gonna run to? I said, Rock, what's the matter with you, Rock?\nWith you, rock. Don't you see I need you, Rock. Don''t love, love.",
